name: Tick
description: Used to assign custom functions to run at every timer interval tick.

name: MouseDown
description: Triggers when the left mousebutton is pressed on the object.

name: MouseUp
description: Triggers when the left mousebutton is raised on the object.

name: Click
description: Triggers when the object is clicked on.

name: DoubleClick
description: Triggers when the object is double clicked on.

name: MouseDown_Right
description: Triggers when the right mousebutton is pressed on the object.

name: MouseUp_Right
description: Triggers when the right mousebutton is raised on the object.

name: DoubleClick_Right
description: Triggers when the object is double clicked on with the right mousebutton.

name: MouseLeave
description: Triggers when the mouse leaves the object area.

name: MouseEnter
description: Triggers when the mouse enters the object area.
